b507b064f295e69523269edade40c5b4f73af49","tid":2024952,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"女記者講述期間，一度情緒激動，需要停下冷靜。她其續指，她醒後，雙手被綁，因她本來是因生理需要進入女廁，當時她已失禁。她向旁邊的警員要水，但警員向她稱「你禮貌啲我就畀你啦！」其後有一名女警把他扶起坐在地上，但用水從高處向她倒下，並要她不斷講「多謝」，而且旁邊有一拆風扇吹向她，並稱是「幫妳降溫」，令她十分寒冷而且昏昏欲睡。她展出相片，顯示她送院時頭部有腫脹。<br />\n<br />\n其他詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200520&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60958914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200520%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60958914&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7kkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=c89591f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200520%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60958914&h=055b16b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200520&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60958914</a>"},{"pid":"56b7021d5093ba46a4d242775673869675c08d74","tid":2024952,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"果兩個少女去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672823f841cf98562dbb244f788cc4760ddc4230","tid":2024952,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"第一身講述， 竟然冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0064d0813260882ef649ab4c4dd568917f58e98","tid":2024952,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj